hcc_text: East 222nd Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At East 222nd Street at New England Thrwy Sb En East 222nd Street and Baychester Avenue, there were 11 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
